      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 25 article about corporate tax shelter abuses, and reference to source of estimate by Treasury Sec Lawrence H Summers for shelters' cost to government</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article in Business Day on Thursday about corporate tax shelter abuses referred imprecisely to the source of an estimate cited by Treasury Secretary Lawrence H. Summers for the shelters' cost to the government. The figure, $10 billion, came from a study by a Stanford University professor; Treasury Department tax analysts have not issued an estimate.</p>
      </block>
